author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
This is the second part of my Ren review and follows Vincent's Tale - Sunflowers (Prologue). 
"Self-Portrait" is an epic seven minutes and if you want to watch it in its entirety first, it can be found here: https://youtu.be/d-myXdYvu3w?si=bg-u7iGGhmtUl7gS
It's also worth checking out the back stories to much of Vincent's Tale by watching these: 
https://youtu.be/vZ1MnVHARME?si=NDwo8q0782tI2JSI
https://youtu.be/TYAnqQ--KX0?si=zLC1zDc6Frr-E1bZ
Ren has also dramatised some of the characters' stories beyond what happens in the videos - they can be watched on his TikTok or Instagram account: https://www.instagram.com/renmakesmusic/?hl=en
**Please note: My Producer asked me to apologise for my chair and to sort it out, but I failed on both counts***

To come and see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, find tickets here: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo message
title: Ren: Squeaking With Excitement....
